{"tid":1575261,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"唔想咁多被自殺案件就入嚟","createTime":"2019-09-16T18:53:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-17T11:33:30.000Z","uid":306587,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8964019fbf577b8c2623a8cd7ecfc24d59997f42","tid":1575261,"uid":306587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T18:53:49.000Z","msg":"近來被自殺事件一單接一單<br />\n啲狗點都會話被自殺嘅人無可疑<br />\n嚟緊相信會有更多被自殺案<br />\n為免各位連登神探未來要用盡人力物力破案<br />\n小弟希望可以同大家玩個<span style=\"color: red;\">我不自殺挑戰</span><br />\n<br />\n遊戲規則:<br />\nTwitter不被自殺運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1570532\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1570532</a><br />\n<br />\n用返呢位巴打嘅idea<br />\n我地可以用ig,facebook之類嘅社交媒體<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1.各位身懷絕技嘅手足<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/GRuinEjpB5M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FGRuinEjpB5M&d=CoEtBkFB9dbfLkjoGL86rT%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=14e3038e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/GRuinEjpB5M</a><br />\n記唔記得呢位武術大師<br />\n<br />\n我依家要挑戰你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n拎起你地嘅遮或者其他工具(球拍,鑊鏟,玩具劍,etc)<br />\n運用你嘅創意,做得比佢更好，更有型<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n喺你嘅po話比你啲朋友知我依家又健康又有自信<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我要陪香港走到最後<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自殺？不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2.各位文靜嘅手足，如果覺得膠的話，其實都可以簡簡單單，用白紙手寫，好以下咁樣:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5yyooqQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5yyooqQ.jpg&h=63dd4ac5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當然唔出樣都得，就咁影張手寫嘅白紙:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u8aeu5t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu8aeu5t.jpg&h=a8a01984&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後嗰一句想指出，我地要對準政權，唔好俾身為傀儡嘅狗模糊焦點 (雖然佢地做過好多仆街嘢)<br />\n<br />\n歡迎喺白紙上加上其他對白<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3.無論邊種方法最後記得加返hashtag:若然我自殺,兇手是警察。 幕後黑手是中國。<br />\n#2019idonotsuicidechallengehk<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n4.再tag或者share俾3個或以上嘅朋友<br />\n<br />\n當然有英文版會更好，但小弟需要大家幫忙翻譯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個挑戰無論勇武定和理非都可以參與㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小弟都希望可以喺度拋磚引玉，等各位高手俾更啲吸引人參與嘅方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你話我玩膠又好，諗埋啲無聊嘢都好<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[red]最緊要喺唔好再俾狗有藉口被自殺手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[red]</span>"},{"pid":"4bccc71d76ea82adfaacf86eb6d77ca4ce0bc3fa","tid":1575261,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T18:54:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pvsTHEi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpvsTHEi.jpg&h=e8bfe3ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">星期三有大綱睇</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">宣佈 和你suck 4.0 9月22 星期日見<br />\n<br />\nsuck 4.0 將會基於 hkmap.live 行動  <br />\n麻煩力推呢個livemap <br />\n對各位日後行動都非常大幫助<br />\n<br />\n請各位必須係 9月22日當日12點30分留意channel / 連登 / IG 最新消息<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n連登post:<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1568754\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1568754</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n TG : <a href=\"https://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=CoEtBkFB9dbfLkjoGL86rT%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=28a64911\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n<br />\nIG : <a href=\"https://instagram.com/suck.withyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fsuck.withyou&d=CoEtBkFB9dbfLkjoGL86rT%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=f02db479\" data-auto-link target=\"_blan